Place the jars in forTomcatLib folder into your Tomcat server -- lib folder

NOTE: 
The below steps are not mandatory, but at times when the local tomcat server location 
points to "Use workspace metadat" then there might be an error while you run the project
like the implementation class not found (because the class files might not be generated on the server)
To resolve the error point the tomcat to "Use Tomcat installation" option ... :) 